<p><b>Hyperhidrosis</b> is the condition characterized by abnormally increased <a href="/wiki/Perspiration" title="Perspiration">perspiration</a>,<sup id="cite_ref-Andrews_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Andrews-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup> in excess of that required for regulation of <a href="/wiki/Body_temperature" title="Body temperature" class="mw-redirect">body temperature</a>.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
